{
  "texts": [
    "ALCOHOL -ABUSE: Strategies: Female: No more than 1 drink in a single day and no more than 7 drinks per week.",
    "Male: No more than 2 drinks in a single day and no more than 14 drinks per week 1. Review clinical notes for mentions of alcohol intake frequency, quantity, or patterns. 2.",
    "Check for records of discussions, interventions, or counseling sessions specifically addressing alcohol consumption. 2.",
    "If troponin levels are mentioned, check if they are elevated.",
    "If so, the criterion is met. 3."
  ]
}